<h2>Changes Requested</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @creator.first_name %>,</p>

<p>Our team has reviewed your uploaded asset "<strong><%= @asset.original_filename || @asset.asset_type.titleize %></strong>" for the campaign "<strong><%= @campaign.title %></strong>" and has requested some changes.</p>

<% if @asset.admin_notes.present? %>
  <p><strong>Notes from the team:</strong></p>
  <blockquote style="border-left: 3px solid #6366F1; padding-left: 12px; color: #555;">
    <%= @asset.admin_notes %>
  </blockquote>
<% end %>

<p>Please log in to your Creators Portal to upload a revised version.</p>

<p>— The Launch Team</p>
